# Personal Overrides (not committed to git)
#
# Copy this file to CLAUDE.local.md and customize for your local setup.
# CLAUDE.local.md is gitignored — it won't affect other team members.
#
# Examples of what goes here:
# - Editor-specific conventions
# - Local file paths or environment quirks
# - Workflow preferences (e.g., always show diffs before committing)
#
# For paths that offer a language choice (B, C, D), you can record that
# preference here too — but Path A is JS-only and Path E has no code,
# so language preferences don't apply universally.

## My Preferences

- When generating output, include timestamps in filenames
- Before any git commit, show me the diff and wait for confirmation
